The autobuild cookbooks are an addition to the cook distribution
and implement a build system intended for large scale development
projects. Features include:

  o  Automated dependency detection
  o  Reliable incremental builds
  o  RPM packing support
  o  Third party package support
  o  Java/maven handoff

... and much more. For further information, see http://www.cg-soft.com/tools/build


For a quick demo, run the following commands after unpacking this tarfile:

% ./configure
% make
% cd examples
% ../bin/b install


